33#ifndef _DIS_TABLES_H
34#define _DIS_TABLES_H
35
36/*
37 * Constants and prototypes for the IA32 disassembler backend. See dis_tables.c
38 * for usage information and documentation.
39 */
40
41#ifdef __cplusplus
42extern "C" {
43#endif
44
45#include <sys/types.h>
46#include <sys/proc.h>
47#include <sys/param.h>
48
49/*
50 * values for cpu mode
51 */
52#define SIZE16 1
53#define SIZE32 2
54#define SIZE64 3
55
56#define OPLEN 256
57#define PFIXLEN 8
58#define NCPS 20 /* number of chars per symbol */
59
60/*
61 * data structures that must be provided to dtrace_dis86()
62 */
63typedef struct d86opnd {
64 char d86_opnd[OPLEN]; /* symbolic rep of operand */
65 char d86_prefix[PFIXLEN]; /* any prefix string or "" */
66 uint_t d86_mode; /* mode for immediate */
67 uint_t d86_value_size; /* size in bytes of d86_value */
68 uint64_t d86_value; /* immediate value of opnd */
69} d86opnd_t;
70
71typedef struct dis86 {
72 uint_t d86_mode;
73 uint_t d86_error;
74 uint_t d86_len; /* instruction length */
75 int d86_rmindex; /* index of modrm byte or -1 */
76 uint_t d86_memsize; /* size of memory referenced */
77 char d86_bytes[16]; /* bytes of instruction */
78 char d86_mnem[OPLEN];
79 uint_t d86_numopnds;
80 uint_t d86_rex_prefix; /* value of REX prefix if !0 */
81 char *d86_seg_prefix; /* segment prefix, if any */
82 uint_t d86_opnd_size;
83 uint_t d86_addr_size;
84 uint_t d86_got_modrm;
85 uint_t d86_vsib; /* Has a VSIB */
86 struct d86opnd d86_opnd[4]; /* up to 4 operands */
87 int (*d86_check_func)(void *);
88 int (*d86_get_byte)(void *);
89#ifdef DIS_TEXT
90 int (*d86_sym_lookup)(void *, uint64_t, char *, size_t);
91 int (*d86_sprintf_func)(char *, size_t, const char *, ...);
92 int d86_flags;
93 uint_t d86_imm_bytes;
94#endif
95 void *d86_data;
96} dis86_t;
97
98extern int dtrace_disx86(dis86_t *x, uint_t cpu_mode);
99
100#define DIS_F_OCTAL 0x1 /* Print all numbers in octal */
101#define DIS_F_NOIMMSYM 0x2 /* Don't print symbols for immediates (.o) */
102
103#ifdef DIS_TEXT
104extern void dtrace_disx86_str(dis86_t *x, uint_t cpu_mode, uint64_t pc,
105 char *buf, size_t len);
106#endif
107
108#ifdef __cplusplus
109}
110#endif
111
112#endif /* _DIS_TABLES_H */
113
